前果個咩巴黎氣候協議一樣又係左膠送錢比中國洗"},{"pid":"7f4421dc49b20588a262138865233e546fc8a4e3","tid":866882,"uid":83623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:53:55.000Z","msg":"係postal treaty 下允許中國印度唔洗比電子資料比USPS，USPS 係中國收件時要人手查件，因為數量多難以全檢查，而比中國企業利用寄毒品或者違禁品，萬國郵件又無改革打算，中國又默許製毒出口去西方，直接毒害美國人，比中國玩壞10幾年而家仲留係入面已經遲啦"},{"pid":"3e2a1fbdc2629f2e2995c47310a967d6a69a7bdf","tid":866882,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d65c9027d15cf8e2f3e9a18b73cbdce4ef415c3c","tid":866882,"uid":28279,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:22:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來做發展中國家咁多著數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:54:44.000Z","msg":"所以支那成日自稱發展中囉"},{"pid":"f54e302a78f063f87b3e58bfd82aefb49fd8eb82","tid":866882,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4429007cd23b3dac04a1478911bcfa2acdf6edff","tid":866882,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:49:40.000Z","msg":"之前果個咩巴黎氣候協議一樣又係左膠送錢比中國洗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T11:14:05.000Z","msg":"跟住繼續排放無理過"},{"pid":"3a13e59a8c96616b44ea1a39db15138a7669ff4b","tid":866882,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T11:16:09.000Z","msg":"侵：美國都係發展中國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac1a27a62bc53f0d1dfc603c519e073dd5c9f0a","tid":866882,"uid":199540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f4421dc49b20588a262138865233e546fc8a4e3","tid":866882,"uid":83623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:53:55.000Z","msg":"係postal treaty 下允許中國印度唔洗比電子資料比USPS，USPS 係中國收件時要人手查件，因為數量多難以全檢查，而比中國企業利用寄毒品或者違禁品，萬國郵件又無改革打算，中國又默許製毒出口去西方，直接毒害美國人，比中國玩壞10幾年而家仲留係入面已經遲啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T11:17:10.000Z","msg":"新鴉片戰爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}